textBeforeTable: PixelRage. The Patches Scrolls, and Internode Games Network, Gamer's Hell, Gameguru Mania, FileShack, FileFront, ComputerGames.ro, AusGamers, AtomicGamer, 4players.de, Epic Games Forums offer a couple of download links and a complete change list, and the 234 MB patch is mirrored on The first patch for Unreal Tournament 3 is now available, updating Epic's first-person shooter sequel to version 1.1. Word is: "This patch can be applied against English, French, German, Italian and Spanish versions of UT3. Please let me know if you have any questions."
